last_episode_to_air.overview: Anna and Maya are far from where they began. Now all they want is to go back home.

name: PEN15
overview: Middle school as it really happened. Maya Erskine and Anna Konkle star in this adult comedy, playing versions of themselves as thirteen-year-old outcasts in the year 2000, surrounded by actual thirteen-year-olds, where the best day of your life can turn into your worst with the stroke of a gel pen.

episodes.name: First Day
episodes.overview: It’s the first day of seventh grade in the year 2000. School rejects, Anna and Maya, get a lot of unexpected attention.

episodes.name: Miranda
episodes.overview: Maya and Anna become fascinated with the mature girls in their class who smoke. They are faced with the age-old question: stay home and play pretend or go out and do drugs?

episodes.name: Ojichan
episodes.overview: Maya feels a tickle down there which becomes kind of an addiction, distracting her from her best friend who really needs her.

episodes.name: Solo
episodes.overview: Trailview’s Night of Amazing Music is coming up. Anna hopes to win Alex’s heart with a classical aria while Maya is consumed with a lie.

episodes.name: Community Service
episodes.overview: There’s an exclusive fashion show at the local nursing home. Somehow Anna and Maya make it in, but feelings of inadequacy lead them down a shady path.

episodes.name: Posh
episodes.overview: Maya gets a questionable nickname during a school project. Anna goes along with it, resulting in a test of their friendship and identities.

episodes.name: AIM
episodes.overview: Maya and Anna get their very first AIM screennames and their social world opens up. Maybe too much.

episodes.name: Wild Things
episodes.overview: It’s a viewing party to watch the newly released VHS movie, Wild Things. The night gets sexy and Anna and Maya try to keep up.

episodes.name: Anna Ishii-Peters
episodes.overview: Anna gets to sleep over at Maya’s house on a school night and can’t wait to become part of the Ishii-Peter family. But things turn as Anna gets a little too comfortable.

episodes.name: Dance
episodes.overview: It’s the night of their first school dance but Anna and Maya are on bad terms. They’ll have to navigate this unfamiliar terrain set to billboard hits, by themselves.

episodes.name: Pool
episodes.overview: Two days after the dance, Maya and Anna reluctantly go to a lame pool party. A crush unexpectedly shows up, causing them to question their sanity and reputations.

episodes.name: Wrestle
episodes.overview: Maya zeros in on her crush, while Anna deals with the fallout from her parents’ divorce. Together they find outlets in an unexpected extracurricular activity.

episodes.name: Vendy Wiccany
episodes.overview: Anna and Maya discover secret powers within, allowing them to control rocky aspects of their lives through magic.

episodes.name: Three
episodes.overview: Witnessing their daughters reach a new low, Kathy and Yuki rally around them. At school, Maya and Anna receive an opportunity at redemption but it will come with a range of influences.

episodes.name: Sleepover
episodes.overview: Maura hosts a group sleepover at her house. The clock chimes late into the night as secrets and masks threaten the death of friendships.

episodes.name: Play
episodes.overview: The school play has been cast. Maya has the opportunity to get her actual first kiss. Anna struggles to find herself.

episodes.name: Opening Night
episodes.overview: It’s opening night. Hearts are exposed, forcing both Anna and Maya to grow up.

episodes.name: Jacuzzi
episodes.overview: On vacation with Curtis, Anna and Maya are introduced to new crippling insecurities. The girls try to ignore them, but a mystical turn makes their self-doubt impossible to forget.

episodes.name: Bat Mitzvah
episodes.overview: An upcoming Bat Mitzvah forces Maya to face a realization about her family's socio economic status while Anna grapples with an existential crisis.

episodes.name: Shadow
episodes.overview: Anna helps her dad move into an apartment. Maya is confronted by a surprise visitor from Japan.

episodes.name: Yuki
episodes.overview: A day in the life of Yuki.

episodes.name: Grammy
episodes.overview: A new family member comes to live with Anna but their arrival brings unexpected endings. Maya gets a diagnosis.

episodes.name: Luminaria
episodes.overview: Anna and Maya attend the local “Walk For Cancer.” Opportunities for socializing evolve into inklings of mortality.

episodes.name: Runaway
episodes.overview: Anna is given the opportunity of a lifetime but when her parents won’t let her partake, Maya encourages them to take fate into their own hands and embark on a dangerous journey.

episodes.name: Home
episodes.overview: Anna and Maya are far from where they began. Now all they want is to go back home.
